title: Windows 10 Magnet Link not working
body:
## Expected behavior

I expected to click on the windows magnet link to download deepfacelab and have a program be installed or to be redirected to a new page/window.

## Actual behavior

When I click on the link. literally nothing happens. It shows on the reload option that for one moment something is reacting to my clicking on the link, to immediately return to normal with nothing happening, no programs getting installed, and no new windows opening.

## Steps to reproduce

Literally just click the magnet link as far as I know.

## Other relevant information

I have found a thread here that apparently solves this problem, but it has since been closed off to anyone not paying for some reason.
I have literally no experience coding or anything of the sort, I just think deepfakes seem cool and would like to try to make one. 
I have opened and closed the page, restarted my computer, and tried again and again at different times with no results.
My operating system is windows 10.
I'm following a few online guides that all say to click the magnet link if you're on windows 10.
